    {
      "chinese": "有一個禮拜天，阿公、阿嬤與孫子在工寮生火，烤肉和地瓜，煮野菜龍葵湯。孫子就問說：「阿公，我的爸爸、媽媽在哪裡？為什麼我都看不到？」",
      "ab": "maki qutux hngawan ryax, nyan pnahu kya cka saliq yutas, yaki ki laqi cipaq. ro cmuling syam, ptatah ngahi, ki tmahuk ayang yahux. kmayal qa laqi maha, “yutas, yaki, wayal inu yaba yaya mu ya? cwa mu ini ktali krryax?”",
